snippet.title: Chessie Chicken Trailer
snippet.description:
Help Chessie Chicken cross the Chessboards in this fun and unique learning tool for the popular game of Chess. Improve your Chessboard awareness by avoiding squares that can be attacked by a piece on the board.

www.chessiechicken.com
www.omegabyte.tech
